chat.msg: hi there! que comience el juego!!

dirígete hacia la isla del tigre pasando por encima del tronco del árbol, también hacia la isla de los loros, rodéala desde arriba y luego cruza las dos piedras hacia la isla de las ranas.  pasa por debajo de la rana antes de volver sobre tus pasos hacia el cocodrilo para cruzar hacia la piedra negra. Luego dirígete hacia las dos piedras para cruzar hacia la jirafa, rodéala desde abajo hacia el tronco del árbol hasta la serpiente, crúzala para llegar al tesoro.

¡bien, aquí vamos! estoy en la isla del tigre ahora. me dirijo al sur, hacia la isla del loro sin molestar al gran gato. he rodeado la isla del loro por arriba. ahora estoy cruzando hacia la isla de la rana a través de las dos piedras. aquí se ve bonito con todos esos lirios de agua. estoy pasando por debajo de la rana ahora, este lugar está lleno de insectos. luego voy hacia atrás a la isla del cocodrilo

cruzando a la piedra negra, espero que el cocodrilo no este de humor para un bocadillo. estoy dirigiéndome a las dos piedras para cruzar hacia el lugar de la jirafa. ¿debería retroceder si la jirafa se pone territorial? de todos modos, rodeo la isla de la jirafa por abajo, llegando al tronco del árbol. finalmente, estoy en la isla de la serpiente. está tranquila ahora, por suerte. cruzaré a la isla del tesoro. ¡yupi! he encontrado el tesoro. *finished*
hola, q tal? ready to start?
yes
great! just go a few steps to the left, head toward the florist stand, but don't reach it
then take a sharp u-turn back towards that cute white dog. neat, right?
yeah
cool! now, just stroll straight south until you find another white dog
he's chilling next to a checkered picnic mat
done
fantastic! now, walk over that mat and head west
oh, and give those berries a touch, why don't you?
done
cool! now see that wooden branch? cross over it to the north
done
great! now navigate around that green bush to the right until you reach the florist stand
don't touch the bush, though!
i walked a bit on the grass sadly, but i'm done
no problem, happens to the best of us! now, take a left from the stand and stroll towards a bridge with two cyclists, passing it to the west
c'est fait
awsome job! now, just past the bridge, you'll see a pair of old folks reading newspapers
head a bit south, will ya?
c'est fait
perfect! now stroll east, between the branch and a green bush
hola, you ready?
Yes
great! i'm in a tent at the top of the map
where to now?
descend vers le chien en contournant celui-ci par la gauche et sans toucher le buisson ou les rochers
alrighty, just passed the dog on the left, avoiding bushes and rocks
what's next, my friend?
go east from under the dog to the fire, stop before touching it
okay, traveled east to the fire, stopped before touching it
what next, buddy?
contourne par le haut le feu puis passe sous les champignons jusqu'à te rapprocher de la voiture sans l'atteindre
got it, passed the fire from the top, went under the mushrooms and got close to the car but didn't touch it
reviens sur tes pas en suivant le chemin vers l'ouest puis le sud jusqu'à la lunette d'observation sans la toucher
followed your instructions! went back west then south and now i'm close to the telescope, didn't touch it though
passe entre le téléscope et le buisson vers le sud pour rejoindre le chemin
check, went between the telescope and the bush to the south, back on the path now
continue le chemin vers l'ouest puis monte doucement à travers les rochers jusqu'à la cabane de bois
did as you said! went west then slowly climbed up through the rocks and now, i'm at the wooden house
*finished* dude!
hey there, estas listo?
je suis prêt
great! first, head under the first palm tree towards the south-west, then make a right at the second tree
just before you reach the third tree, take a sharp left and keep moving south
repête en anglais s'il te plait
no problem, mate
before hitting the third tree, take a sharp left and go straight south
done i think
nice job! now, see that brown puppy on your left? take a soft left and then a right so we're heading south again
done
perfect! now move between the big rock on your left and the smaller one on your right
you'll reach the water's edge
c'est fait
good job! now, wade a little into the water until you spot a large red crab
once you see it, make a right and follow the big rock, keeping it on your left side. go west, mate
voilà
well done! next, enter the water till you come across a medium rock, just after that there's a shark
give my regards and turn sharply to your right
je crois que c'est bon
awesome! now head back to the land, pass between the medium rock and a multicolored ball, and keep heading north
ok
great! now, slightly veer left and head towards the north-west
you'll cross between a red tent on your left and a bigger speaker on your right
j'y suis
fantastic! now circle around the red tent, keep it on your right side and then head south
done
you're nearly there! at the shoreline, turn right and walk under the red kayak
voilà
you're doing amazing! turn a sharp right, move along the kayak until you reach a small green bush
and voilà!
